\c 13
\p
\v 1 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri, richiti,
\v 2 Mwanakomana womunhu, porofitira vaporofita VaIsraeri vanoporofita, uti kuna ivo vanoporofita zvinobva mumoyo mavo, inzwai imwi shoko raJehovha.
\v 3 Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Vane nhamo vaporofita mapenzi, vanotevera mweya yavo, vasina chavakaona.
\v 4 Aiwa Israeri, vaporofita venyu vakafanana namakava pamatongo.
\v 5 Hamuna kukwira muchipinda pakakoromorwa, kana kugadzira rusvingo rweimba yaIsraeri, kuti mumire pakurwa pazuva raJehovha.
\v 6 Vakaona zvinonyengera nokuporofita kwenhema, ivo vanoti, Jehovha anoti! Asi Jehovha haana kuvatuma, zvino vakati shoko ravo richasimbiswa.
\v 7 Hamuna kuona zvinonyengera here, hamuna kutaura kuvuka kwenhema here, zvamakati, Jehovha anoti; kunyange zvakadaro handina kutaura?
\v 8 Naizvozvo zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Zvamakatura zvinonyengera, nokuona nhema, naizvozvo, tarirai, ndine mhaka nemi, ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe Jehovha.
\v 9 Ruoko rwangu rucharwa navaporofita vanoona zvinonyengera navanoporofita nhema; havangarangani navanhu vangu, havanganyorwi mazita avo parugwaro rweimba yaIsraeri, havangapindi munyika yaIsraeri; zvino muchaziva kuti ndini Ishe Jehovha.
\p
\v 10 Nokuti zvirokwazvo, nokuti vakanyengera vanhu vangu, vachiti: Rugare! Izvo hakuna rugare; kana vovaka rusvingo, tarira, vovuwa nesuko.
\v 11 Chiudza avo vanoruvuwa nesuko, kuti ruchakoromoka; mvura ichauya ichinaya kwazvo, ine, mabwe makuru echimvuramabwe, muchawa, nedutu remhepo urutsemure.
\v 12 Zvino tarirai, kana rusvingo rwakoromoka havangati kwamuri here: Ko suko ramakuvuwa naro riripiko?
\v 13 Naizvozvo zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Ndicharutsemusa zvirokwazvo nedutu remhepo nehasha dzangu; mvura ichanaya kwazvo nokutsamwa kwangu, namabwe makuru echimvuramabwe nehasha dzangu, kurupedza chose.
\v 14 Saizvozvo ndichakoromora rusvingo rwamakavuwa nesuko, nokuruwisira pasi, kusvikira nheyo dzarwo dzafukurwa; ruchakoromoka, nemwi muchaparadzwa mukati marwo; zvino muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha.
\v 15 Saizvozvo ndichapedza hasha dzangu parusvingo, napamusoro pavakaruvuwa nesuko; ndichati kwamuri: Rusvingo haruchipo, navakaruvuwa havachipo;
\v 16 ivo vaporofita VaIsraeri vanoporofita pamusoro peJerusarema, vachirionera zviratidzo zvorugare, izvo hakuna rugare; ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe Jehovha.
\p
\v 17 Asi iwe, mwanakomana womunhu, rinzira chiso chako kuvakunda vavanhu vako, ivo vanoporofita zvinobva mumoyo yavo, uporofite pamusoro pavo,
\v 18 uti: Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Vane nhamo vakadzi vanosonera maziso emaoko, vanoita micheka yokufukidza misoro yavanhu vapi navapi, kuti vavhime mweya. Munoda kuvhima mweya yavanhu vangu, muchida kuzviponesera mweya iyeyo!
\v 19 Makandimhura pakati pavanhu vangu nokuda kwetsama dzebhari nezvimedu zvezvingwa, kuti muuraye mweya isingafaniri kufa, nokuponesa mweya isingafaniri kurarama, muchirevera vanhu vangu nhema, ivo vanoteerera nhema dzenyu.
\v 20 Naizvozvo zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Tarirai, ndine mhaka nezvifukidzo zvenyu zvamunovhima nazvo mweya yavanhu seshiri, ndichazvibvarura pamaoko enyu; ndicharegedza mweya, iyo mweya yamunovhima seshiri.
\v 21 Nemicheka yenyu ndichaibvarurawo, ndirwire vanhu vangu pamaoko enyu, varege kuzova mumaoko enyu kuti muvavhime; zvino muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha.
\v 22 Nokuti nenhema dzenyu makarwadza moyo wowakarurama, wandisina kuchemedza, mukasimbisa maoko owakaipa, kuti arege kudzoka panzira yake yakaipa, aponeswe;
\v 23 naizvozvo hamuchazoonizve zviratidzo zvinonyengera kana kuuka zvinoukwa; ini ndicharwira vanhu vangu pamaoko enyu; zvino muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha.